### SECTION 1: IMPLEMENTATION REPORT (Markdown Format)

# IMPLEMENTATION REPORT

## Coverage Statistics
- Total Requirements: 12
- Implemented: 12  
- Coverage Rate: 100%

## Requirement Mapping
| ID | Requirement | Implementation | Placement | Rationale |
|----|-------------|----------------|-----------|-----------|
| R1 | "2019 MacBook Pro 13-inch - Space Gray - Excellent Condition" heading | `native-text`, `heading-large` style | `Header`, first item |  Clearly identifies the product. |
| R2 | Price: $800 | `native-text`, `heading-medium` style | `Content`, after heading | Prominent display of price. |
| R3 | Condition: Excellent (Minor scratches on the bottom case) | `native-text`, `body` style | `Content`, after price |  Provides important detail about the product's state. |
| R4 | Images: [Carousel of 5-7 high-quality images] | `native-rectangle`, `purpose`: "image-carousel", `aspectRatio`: "16:9", `imageType`: "photo" (Note: Carousel component not available. Horizontal scroll implemented via native elements) | `Content`, after condition | Showcases the product visually.  |
| R5 | Seller Profile: [Seller Avatar], John Doe (5-star rating, 12 reviews) | `native-circle` (`purpose`: "user-avatar", `size`: "medium"), `native-text` (username, rating, reviews) | `Content`, after image carousel | Displays seller credibility and contact information. |
| R6 | Description: "..." | `native-text`, `body` style | `Content`, after seller profile | Detailed information about the product's usage and condition. |
| R7 | Specifications (Processor: ..., RAM: ..., Storage: ..., Graphics: ...) | `native-text`, `body` style,  organized into a list or table | `Content`, after description | Provides key technical specifications. |
| R8 | Primary Actions: "Contact Seller", "Add to Cart" | `component`, `componentId`: "10:3907" (Button, `purpose`: "primary-action", `style`: "filled", `size`: "large", `color`: "primary") x2 | `Content`, after specifications | Primary calls to action for the user. |
| R9 | Secondary Actions: "View Seller Profile", "Report Listing" | `component`, `componentId`: "10:3907" (Button, `purpose`: "secondary-action", `style`: "text", `size`: "medium", `color`: "secondary") x2 | `Header`, after heading, within a horizontal container | Provides additional actions.  |
| R10 | Status Indicators: "Listing Created: 2 days ago", "10 views" | `native-text`, `caption` style | `Content`, below primary actions | Provides contextual information about the listing. |
| R11 | Microcopy: "..." | `native-text`, `caption` style |  Various placements as appropriate within the content section |  Provides user guidance and instructions. |
| R12 | Bottom Navigation (Assuming Mobile App) | `component`, `componentId`: "10:4724" (BottomNav) | Root level, last item |  Standard mobile navigation. |


## Design Decisions
- **Layout Strategy**: Three-section mobile layout (Header, Content,  Footer (BottomNav if mobile)).  Vertical layout used primarily for content sections, horizontal for smaller elements like icon/label pairs.
- **Component Choices**: Utilized system buttons (10:3907) for consistency and native text for flexible content display.  The missing carousel was addressed using horizontal scrolling within a `layoutContainer`.
- **Hierarchy Decisions**: Primary actions are prominently positioned after the product details, while secondary actions are in the header.
- **Gaps Addressed**: No dedicated carousel component exists; implemented using native rectangles and horizontal scrolling.


